              "text": {
                "content": "Out of all models in KT that existed in 2022, Dynamic Key-Value Memory Networks (DKVMN) have been argued to be state-of-the-art. A drawback of these models is that they seem to not consider learning abilities or behavioral features collected by ITS. ",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
